devdoc.details: This contract will hold user scheduled payments which will be released after release time

getBeneficiaryPaymentIds(address).details: Returns all payment ids for beneficiary

getDevWallet().details: returns the dev fund wallet address

getFeesWallet().details: returns the fee receiver wallet address

getSenderPaymentIds(address).details: Returns all payment ids for sender

params.devWallet: Wallet address where dev fund will go
params.feesWallet: Wallet address where fees will go

isFreeToken(address).details: Checks if token is in free list

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

pause().details: Called by an admin to pause, triggers stopped state.

paused().details: Returns true if the contract is paused, and false otherwise.

releasable(uint256).details: Returns whether given payment can be released or not

release(uint256).details: Allows beneficiary of payment to release payment after release time

removeTokenFromFreeList(address).details: called by admin to remove given token from free tokens list

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions anymore. Can only be called by the current owner.     * NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby removing any functionality that is only available to the owner.

scheduleBulkPayment(address,uint256[],ui.details: Allows user to schedule payment. In case of ERC-20 token the user will first have to approve the contract to spend on his/her behalf

params.amounts: List of amount of tokens to pay
params.beneficiaries: List of addresses of the beneficiaries
params.isFeeInSwap: Bool to check if fee to be paid in swap token or not
params.releaseTimes: List of release times after which tokens to be released. In seconds
params.tokenAddress: Address of the token to be paid

params.releaseTime: release time after which tokens to be released. In seconds
params.tokenAddress: Address of the token to be paid

setAllowedFeeSlippagePercentage(uint8).details: Update fee slippage percentage allowance for erc20

params.allowedFeeSlippagePercentage: New allowed fee slippage percentage for fee in erc20

setDevWallet(address).details: Allows admin to set fee receiver wallet

params.ethFeePercentage: New percentage of fee in eth

setFeeWallet(address).details: Allows admin to set fee receiver wallet

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.

unpause().details: Called by an admin to unpause, returns to normal state.
